value.0: Yeah, we know, this will likely end up as a jock strap or G-String... but you can still throw rocks with it.

The Tao of H.A.L.O.

Hells Army of the Lost Order (H.A.L.O.) Neutral evil

Greatly outnumbered and against the orders of the high priest the Imperial Warlords marched into battle as well their certain death. The high priest in a red sea of anger over their defiance cursed each member of the faction to an eternity of servitude in Hell and as each member fell in battle their sentence had begun.

Hell would find its own use for these battle proven warriors and quickly enlisted them with the task of reaping souls on the surface and returning them to the boatman on the great river Styx. Still an ember remained in the Warlords and over time it grew into a flame as the Warlords broke the bonds of hell and returned to Carpathia seeking their revenge.

Having been cursed by the power of the gods of light and walked through the depths of the underworld they have developed their own laws and ways for the laws of men do not carry bonds over those who have already server a sentence in Hell.

The ground breaks and the pit opens. The shrieking of tormented souls is the trumpet that heralds the coming of the tortured ones. Wandering the dark mountains, they are drawn to the dark power of battle. Names forgotten, loyalties burned. The unholy chorus of steel on bone and power used to rend flesh is the only familiar symphony. Wading into battle, ambushing the unwary, one by one they return. Finding shelter and victims in the dark corners of Carpathia, an uneasy living is eeked out of the darkness.

The haze clouding the minds of these lost, yet honorable warriors hides everything. Tormented behind their eyes, sleep is a doorway into madness. This soft world is undeserving. These fattened, pretentious, well funded marauders would not know true battle if it rolled over their sleepy villages. Over time the haze thins. The memories begin creeping back. How to train for the real battle. How this life is just preparatory time for the coming battle. Some have sensed it. Some write of the underworld. Some of the elysian fields. Some talk of Valhalla. One man's heaven is another's hell. The only fluffy clouds in the after life are those from the battle field. Hell has it's legions. It has it's generals. It has a dark, twisted order. It has it's sites set on the realms of light.

Now this world needs order. These lost few have found one another again. They have been bound by blood, hardened by steel and baptized in fire. This is how you know them.

This is the Lost Order.

Hell's Army of the Lost Order has risen again. As they adapt to the soft world of the living, they begin carving the flesh of the weak. No vengeance, No guardian, No Heretics, no followers of the blood or any others will stand in the path of these lost heroes. Not even Hell could keep them. There is no place for them. So they take and make their own.

Once in HALO you are expected to carry yourself with honor. This means one on one battle unless escalated by your opponent. This can also mean your opponent is many levels over you. As we exited hell, we did so as individuals. Thus our individuality is kept. A trophy of our ascent.

We are visitors to this realm, and as was once with Rome, we will follow the rules of the realm in which we reside. We will take as we will but will do so only with honor and audacity.

We will not be mild. Humor, audacity, and individuality mark our guild. We build as we see fit. The traditional man/woman is a puppet of the dusty past and while there are valuable lessons there, the true warrior is like water. Water adapts, and flows forward ever seeking new ways and greater weaknesses.

To quote the great Warrior Bruce Lee:
-The tools, your natural weapons, have a double purpose:

1.) To destroy the opponent in front of you - annihilation of things that stand in the way of peace, justice and humanity.

2.) To destroy your own impulses caused by the instincts of self-preservation. To destroy anything bothering your mind. Not to hurt anyone, but to overcome your own greed, anger and folly. Jeet Kune Do is directed toward oneself.


This is the Tao which is most effective. Respond to your opponent, inside and out, with violence due any threat of any magnitude.

-If you follow the classical pattern, you are understanding the routine, the tradition, the shadow - you are not understanding yourself.

-Understanding oneself happens through a process of relationships and not through isolation.

This is why HALO exists. Because as we met after our trials in the nether region we began to understand who we were. That tiny voice directing us. Bringing us together in the new fire. Some were invited, others requested membership. The false ones will fall away like the scabs of the healing wound.

-Knowledge is fixed in time, whereas, knowing is continual. Knowledge comes from a source, from an accumulation, from a conclusion, while knowing is a movement.

This is the way of operation. There are ways of building that produce known results. There are ways that are yet to be known. We study all things and come to know as we experience.

This is the Tao. The Way. HALO shall not fall from the inside, and will only grow from our conflicts. We have no enemies and we have no allies. Both concepts allow for a given weakness. We kill when opportunity for both advancement or defense present themselves. Be ever prepared for death. You can embrace death as both a gift to be given or received. Do not complain about your death, rather accept it as a lesson. What defeated you? Ultimately, you did. A stronger build exploits a weakness. A group that kills the one will have within itself the key to the one's weakness. The one that kills another one exposes weakness. Do not shout to the world your woes. Thank your killer for a good fight and move on. HALO does not whine. We do not flee the field of battle for simple preservation of self. Death is a transitional phase and that too can be overcome. We learn. We flow. That is the way.

Of course we also taunt. A well placed insult is handy when destroying the spirit of your opponent. But use this sparingly.

Now, march forward into the world and show them that Hell's fury is incarnate upon the land.
